        <updateDate>2021-09-28T21:08:36Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Local Infrastructure Financing Tools Act or the LIFT Act</strong></p> <p>This bill allows the issuer of an American Infrastructure Bond a credit with respect to each interest payment under such bond. </p> <p>The bill restores advance refundings of bonds to allow states and localities to refinance existing debt. </p> <p>The bill increases to $30 million the limitation on bank-qualified debt for small municipal and nonprofit issuers.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
